title: Ceiling Paper, 1875–1925
description: Rose sprig in a beaded circle alternating with rose sprig in a quatrefoil.  These motifs are separated by foliage scrolls imitating woven fabric.  Gold, green, white, liquid mica, and shades of red and pink on a cream ground.

tombstone.epitaph:
Ceiling Paper, 1875–1925.
1875–1925. Machine-printed, mica, liquid. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1352.
